Name: goredo
Version: 1.0.0
Release: alt1

Summary: Go implementation of djb's redo, Makefile replacement that sucks less

Group: Development/Tools
License: GPLv3
Url: http://www.goredo.cypherpunks.ru/index.html

Packager: Vitaly Lipatov <lav@altlinux.ru>

